{"tid":1659682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 十八區文宣組要人！","createTime":"2019-10-17T05:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T06:48:59.000Z","uid":130207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e60fe4f574c6772709bb47d796acac3118a9a0b","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"岑子杰當街比人用鐵鎚打頭 甚至蒙面法<br />\n對家嘅目的為左製造政治白色恐怕<br />\n令所有人都驚 唔敢再出嚟<br />\n我地10月20更加要出嚟 比國際比777睇香港人未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往民陣100萬 200萬 甚至流水式遊行<br />\n都會有唔少文宣組起街上派傳單 吸納更多唔同層面嘅和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個星期我個人觀察 幾乎係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無人咁做</span></span></span><br />\n文宣傳單組！！出嚟呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">行動建議：</span></span><br />\n自行組成<span style=\"color: gold;\">2-3人小組</span>形式<br />\n每日<span style=\"color: gold;\">4點到7點</span><br />\n去自己最熟悉社區人流高嘅位置<br />\n每人派200張（黑白彩色Size自己衡量） <br />\n一個鐘內好快派完<br />\n<br />\n如非必要 唔好自己一個行動<br />\n到達選定目標地方後<br />\n用三分鐘觀察及計劃逃生路線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手推行動post<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agyoK3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagyoK3L.jpg&h=42f708f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GnygkB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnygkB5.jpg&h=519d8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0tTnQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0tTnQr.jpg&h=0ca2abc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qangas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qangas.jpg&h=72a3d4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5d8j2Qt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5d8j2Qt.jpg&h=35ea38d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"788c3acea2baaa6897bfd28dc4cce08a606b2190","tid":1659682,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"溫馨提示 <br />\n和理非大遊行<br />\n政府從來冇俾過屎<br />\n又要吹風和理非<br />\n又幫林鄭手止暴制亂<br />\n林鄭真係多謝你都嚟唔切<br />\n唔記得818和理非完咗<br />\n畀政府撚狗咁撚<br />\n讚你乖乖仔<br />\n仲要吹風裝都唔帶?<br />\n又想好似929咁樣害啲手足食tg,著短褲打到仆街?"},{"pid":"26d64e1724242258b4bb3a1867e99b1aa52d0427","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"80810459ef70d546067e19c7c4ab01bbe05614fe","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0278e8b2d89e5c36b7f1c6d5993a632e364c7b77","tid":1659682,"uid":176999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ef97bd263b63c3943340b4a239327c5156f2365","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"十連無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35d9ea13d86067f1d6558822e3235f1651fb290","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea572d9fee79d75f5568ce7836478185ef5098c","tid":1659682,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59f303f93da629e9be3c3209e0e5f245019e59f6","tid":1659682,"uid":130207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"推到核爆"},{"pid":"9040f4353c70d06e14d1a30fb85e975df8fb7a83","tid":1659682,"uid":181659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><